<i>noun</i>: 폭발음 [폭빠름], 폭발 [폭빨] <i>verb</i>: 폭발하다 [폭빨하다], 폭발시키다 [폭빨시키다], 발파하다 [발파하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>폭발음 [폭빠름]</dt><br>
<dd>sound of explosion; blast</dd><br>
<dd>폭발할 때 나는 큰 소리.</dd><br>
<dd>A loud sound made when something explodes.</dd><br>
<dt>폭발 [폭빨]</dt><br>
<dd>explosion; blast</dd><br>
<dd>불이 일어나며 갑자기 터짐.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of a fire rising and exploding suddenly.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>폭발하다 [폭빨하다]</dt><br>
<dd>explode; blast</dd><br>
<dd>불이 일어나며 갑자기 터지다.</dd><br>
<dd>For a fire to rise and explode suddenly.</dd><br>
<dt>폭발시키다 [폭빨시키다]</dt><br>
<dd>explode; blast</dd><br>
<dd>불이 일어나며 갑자기 터지게 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To make a fire rise and explode suddenly.</dd><br>
<dt>발파하다 [발파하다]</dt><br>
<dd>blast; blow up</dd><br>
<dd>바위나 단단한 물체에 구멍을 뚫고 폭약을 넣어서 폭파시키다.</dd><br>
<dd>To drill a hole into a rock or solid object, put an explosive into the hole, and then blow it up.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>